<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>Launch the Pulse server application. </li>
            <li>In the Pulse Server Configuration window, select the <span class="Emphasis">General</span> tab.</li>
            <li>In the SQL&#160;Server area, review the Server Name and Databases that were configured during installation.</li>
            <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Test</span>.</li>
            <li>If the test is successful, the system shows a message indicating this.</li>
            <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">OK</span> to close the message. </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>